module.exports = {"type":"REST","title":"下單","en":"Place order","api":{"uri":"/openApi/swap/v2/trade/order","method":"POST","rate-limitation":"10/second","ip-rate-limitation":"3","payload":[{"title":"MARKET","desc":"Place an order at market price and set a take profit","payload":{"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"BUY","positionSide":"LONG","type":"MARKET","quantity":5,"takeProfit":"{\"type\": \"TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET\", \"stopPrice\": 31968.0,\"price\": 31968.0,\"workingType\":\"MARK_PRICE\"}"}},{"title":"STOP_MARKET","desc":"Market stop loss order","payload":{"type":"STOP_MARKET","stopPrice":50000,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"SELL","quantity":0.002,"positionSide":"LONG","clientOrderID":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","workingType":"","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET","desc":"Market price take profit order","payload":{"type":"TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET","stopPrice":70000,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"SELL","quantity":0.002,"positionSide":"LONG","clientOrderID":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","workingType":"","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"STOP","desc":"Stop limit order","payload":{"type":"STOP","price":50000,"stopPrice":50000,"priceRate":0,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"SELL","quantity":0.002,"positionSide":"LONG","clientOrderID":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","workingType":"","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"TAKE_PROFIT","desc":"Limit price and take profit order","payload":{"type":"TAKE_PROFIT","price":70000,"stopPrice":70000,"priceRate":0,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"SELL","quantity":0.002,"positionSide":"LONG","clientOrderID":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","workingType":"","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"TRIGGER_LIMIT","desc":"Limit order with trigger","payload":{"type":"TRIGGER_LIMIT","price":70000,"stopPrice":70000,"priceRate":0,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"BUY","quantity":0.002,"positionSide":"LONG","clientOrderID":"","takeProfit":"","recvWindow":1000,"stopLoss":"","timeInForce":"GTC","workingType":"","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"TRIGGER_MARKET","desc":"Market order with trigger","payload":{"type":"TRIGGER_MARKET","stopPrice":70000,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"BUY","quantity":0.002,"positionSide":"LONG","clientOrderID":"","takeProfit":"","recvWindow":1000,"stopLoss":"","timeInForce":"GTC","workingType":"","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"TRAILING_STOP_MARKET","desc":"Trailing Stop Market Order","payload":{"type":"TRAILING_STOP_MARKET","price":0,"stopPrice":0,"priceRate":0.1,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"BUY","quantity":0.002,"positionSide":"LONG","clientOrderID":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","workingType":"","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"TRAILING_TP_SL","desc":"Trailing TakeProfit or StopLoss","payload":{"type":"TRAILING_TP_SL","price":0,"stopPrice":0,"priceRate":0.1,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"SELL","quantity":0.002,"positionSide":"LONG","clientOrderID":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","workingType":"","timestamp":1726231037325}},{"title":"POSITION_STOP_MARKET","desc":"Market price position stop loss order","payload":{"type":"STOP_MARKET","closePosition":true,"stopPrice":50000,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"SELL","quantity":0.002,"positionSide":"LONG","clientOrderID":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","workingType":"","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"POSITION_TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET","desc":"Market price position take profit order","payload":{"type":"TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET","closePosition":true,"stopPrice":70000,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"SELL","quantity":0.002,"positionSide":"LONG","clientOrderID":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","workingType":"","timestamp":1726223068783}}],"responseBody":{"code":0,"msg":"","data":{"order":{"symbol":"BTC-USDT","orderId":1735950529123455000,"side":"BUY","positionSide":"LONG","type":"MARKET","clientOrderId":"","workingType":"MARK_PRICE"}}},"request":{"info":["<div>基於訂單 type 不同，強制要求某些參數:</div>","<div><li>LIMIT: 強制要求參數 quantity, price</li></div>","<div><li>MARKET: 強制要求參數 quantity</li></div>","<div><li>TRAILING_STOP_MARKET（追跡委託單）和TRAILING_TP_SL（移動止盈止損單）：需填寫price欄位或者priceRate欄位</li></div>","<div><li>TRIGGER_LIMIT, STOP, TAKE_PROFIT: 強制要求參數 quantity、stopPrice、price</li></div>","<div><li>STOP_MARKET, TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET, TRIGGER_MARKET: 強制要求參數 quantity、stopPrice</li></div>","<div>條件單的觸發必須:</div>","<div><h3>STOP/STOP_MARKET 止損單:</h3></div>","<div><li>已掛止損單累加數量不能大於持倉數量</li></div>","<div><li>買入: 標記價格高於等於觸發價stopPrice</li></div>","<div><li>賣出: 標記價格低於等於觸發價stopPrice</li></div>","<div><h3>TAKE_PROFIT/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET 止盈單:</h3></div>","<div><li>已掛止盈單累加數量不能大於持倉數量</li></div>","<div><li>買入: 標記價格低於等於觸發價stopPrice</li></div>","<div><li>賣出: 標記價格高於等於觸發價stopPrice</li></div>","<div>最小下單數量可從接口 /openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts 獲取:tradeMinQuantity、tradeMinUSDT</div>","<div><b>交易規則:</b></div>","<div><a href='https://bingx.com/zh-tw/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/' target='_blank'>https://bingx.com/zh-tw/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/</a></div>","<div>關於價格精度和數量精度參考接口: <a href='https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts' target='_blank'>https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts</a></div>","<div>如果精度超過當期的範圍，當前API下單仍然成功，但是會被截斷.比如price要求是:0.0001,如果下單0.123456.最後會以0.1234成功提交</div>"],"info_en":["<div>Depending on the order type, certain parameters are mandatory:</div>","<div><li>LIMIT: Mandatory Parameters: quantity, price</li></div>","<div><li>MARKET: Mandatory Parameters: quantity</li></div>","<div><li>TRAILING_STOP_MARKET (Tracking Stop Loss Order) or TRAILING_TP_SL (Trailing TakeProfit/StopLoss Order): The price field or priceRate field needs to be filled in</li></div>","<div><li>TRIGGER_LIMIT, STOP, TAKE_PROFIT: Mandatory Parameters: quantity, stopPrice, price</li></div>","<div><li>STOP_MARKET, TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET, TRIGGER_MARKET: Mandatory Parameters: quantity, stopPrice</li></div>","<div>The triggering of the conditional order must:</div>","<div><h3>STOP/STOP_MARKET stop loss order:</h3></div>","<div><li>The accumulative quantity of the pending stop loss orders cannot be greater than the quantity of open positions</li></div>","<div><li>Buy: the mark price is higher than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li></div>","<div><li>Sell: the mark price is lower than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li></div>","<div><h3>TAKE_PROFIT/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET take profit order:</h3></div>","<div><li>The accumulative quantity of the pending take profit order cannot be greater than the position quantity</li></div>","<div><li>Buy: the mark price is lower than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li></div>","<div><li>Sell: the mark price is higher than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li></div>","<div>The minimum order quantity can be obtained from the api /openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts: tradeMinQuantity, tradeMinUSDT</div>","<div><b>Trading Rules:</b></div>","<div><a href='https://bingx.com/zh-tw/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/' target='_blank'>https://bingx.com/zh-tw/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/</a></div>","<div>For price precision and quantity precision, please refer to: <a href='https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts' target='_blank'>https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts</a></div>","<div>If the precision exceeds the allowed range, the API order will still be accepted but the value will be truncated. For example, if the required price precision is 0.0001 and you place an order at 0.123456, it will be submitted as 0.1234.</div>"],"list":[{"name":"symbol","type":"string","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"交易對, 例如: BTC-USDT, 請使用大寫字母","en":"There must be a hyphen/ \"-\" in the trading pair symbol. eg: BTC-USDT"},{"name":"type","type":"string","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"LIMIT：限價單/MARKET：市價單/STOP_MARKET：市價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET：市價止盈單/STOP：限價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT：限價止盈單/TRIGGER_LIMIT：計劃委託單限價單/TRIGGER_MARKET：計劃委託市價單/TRAILING_STOP_MARKET:追踪委託單/TRAILING_TP_SL:移動止盈止損","en":"LIMIT: Limit Order / MARKET: Market Order / STOP_MARKET: Stop Market Order / TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET: Take Profit Market Order / STOP: Stop Limit Order / TAKE_PROFIT: Take Profit Limit Order / TRIGGER_LIMIT: Stop Limit Order with Trigger / TRIGGER_MARKET: Stop Market Order with Trigger / TRAILING_STOP_MARKET: Trailing Stop Market Order / TRAILING_TP_SL: Trailing TakeProfit or StopLoss"},{"name":"side","type":"string","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"買賣方向 SELL, BUY","en":"buying and selling direction SELL, BUY"},{"name":"positionSide","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"持仓方向，单项持仓必填BOTH，双向持仓僅可選擇 LONG 或 SHORT，為空時默認LONG","en":"Position direction, required for single position as BOTH, for both long and short positions only LONG or SHORT can be chosen, defaults to LONG if empty"},{"name":"reduceOnly","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"true, false; 單項持倉模式下默認false；雙開持倉模式下不接受此參數","en":"true, false; Default value is false for single position mode; This parameter is not accepted for both long and short positions mode"},{"name":"price","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"委託價格，TRAILING_STOP_MARKET和TRAILING_TP_SL類型傳該參數表示回撤價差","en":"Price, represents the trailing stop distance in TRAILING_STOP_MARKET and TRAILING_TP_SL"},{"name":"quantity","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"下單數量,合約數量，當前只支持以幣計的合約數，暫不支持用U的數量下單","en":"Original quantity, only support units by COIN ,Ordering with quantity U is not currently supported."},{"name":"quoteOrderQty","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"下單金額, 例如: 100USDT,如果quantity 和 quoteOrderQty 同時輸入，優先使用quantity，quoteOrderQty會被丟棄","en":"Quote order quantity, e.g., 100USDT,if quantity and quoteOrderQty are input at the same time, quantity will be used first, and quoteOrderQty will be discarded"},{"name":"stopPrice","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"觸發價, 僅 STOP_MARKET,TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET,STOP,TAKE_PROFIT,TRIGGER_LIMIT,TRIGGER_MARKET 需要此參數","en":"Trigger price, only required for STOP_MARKET, TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET, STOP, TAKE_PROFIT, TRIGGER_LIMIT, TRIGGER_MARKET"},{"name":"priceRate","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"針對type:TRAILING_STOP_MARKET和TRAILING_TP_SL； 最大：1","en":"For type: TRAILING_STOP_MARKET or TRAILING_TP_SL; Maximum: 1"},{"name":"workingType","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"stopPrice觸發價價格類型：MARK_PRICE、CONTRACT_PRICE、INDEX_PRICE，默認MARK_PRICE。當type為STOP或STOP_MARKET，以及stopGuaranteed為true的時候，workingType只能為CONTRACT_PRICE。","en":"The stopPrice trigger price type can be MARK_PRICE, CONTRACT_PRICE, or INDEX_PRICE, with the default set to MARK_PRICE. When the order type is STOP or STOP_MARKET and stopGuaranteed = true, the workingType can only be set to CONTRACT_PRICE."},{"name":"timestamp","type":"int64","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"請求的時間戳，單位:毫秒","en":"Support setting take profit while placing an order. Only supports type: TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET/TAKE_PROFIT"},{"name":"stopLoss","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"支持下單同時設置止損。但僅支持type: STOP_MARKET/STOP","en":"StopPrice trigger price types: MARK_PRICE, CONTRACT_PRICE, INDEX_PRICE, default MARK_PRICE. When the type is STOP or STOP_MARKET, and stopGuaranteed is true, the workingType must only be CONTRACT_PRICE."},{"name":"takeProfit","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"支持下單同時設置止盈。但僅支持type: TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET/TAKE_PROFIT","en":"request timestamp, unit: millisecond"},{"name":"clientOrderId","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"用戶自定義訂單ID，系統會將該字段轉為英文小寫，限制字符長度1-40,不同訂單不可使用相同的clientOrderId， clientOrderId 僅支援 LIMIT/MARKET 訂單類型","en":"Customized order ID for users, with a limit of characters from 1 to 40. The system will convert this field to lowercase. Different orders cannot use the same clientOrderId, clientOrderId only supports LIMIT/MARKET order type"},{"name":"recvWindow","type":"int64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"請求有效時間空窗值, 單位:毫秒","en":"Request valid time window value, Unit: milliseconds"},{"name":"timeInForce","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"有效方式，目前支持PostOnly、GTC、IOC和FOK","en":"Time in Force, currently supports PostOnly, GTC, IOC, and FOK"},{"name":"closePosition","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"true, false；觸發後全部平倉，僅支援STOP_MARKET和TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET；不與quantity合用；自帶只平倉效果，不與reduceOnly 合用","en":"true, false; all position squaring after triggering, only support STOP_MARKET and TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET; not used with quantity; comes with only position squaring effect, not used with reduceOnly"},{"name":"activationPrice","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"追蹤委託單/移動止盈止損單啟動價格，TRAILING_TP_SL和TRAILING_STOP_MARKET 需要此參數, 預設為下單當前市場價格(支援不同workingType)","en":"Used with TRAILING_STOP_MARKET or TRAILING_TP_SL orders, default as the latest price(supporting different workingType)"},{"name":"stopGuaranteed","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"true：啟用保證止盈停損功能；false：不啟用保證停損功能；cutfee:啟用保證停損功能，同時啟用VIP保證停損費用減免功能，VIP費用減免只有在停損單時才起作用。預設不啟用保證止盈止損功能。stopGuaranteed為true或cutfee的時候，quantity字段不生效。支援的訂單類型type有：STOP_MARKET：市價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET：市價止盈單/STOP：限價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT：限價止盈單/TRIGGER_LIMIT：計劃委託單限價單/TRIGGER_MARKET：計劃計劃委託市價單。","en":"true: Enables the guaranteed stop-loss and take-profit feature; false: Disables the feature; cutfee: Enable the guaranteed stop loss function and enable the VIP guaranteed stop loss fee reduction function. When stopGuaranteed is true or cutfee, the quantity field does not take effect. The guaranteed stop-loss feature is not enabled by default. Supported order types include: STOP_MARKET: Market stop-loss order / TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET: Market take-profit order / STOP: Limit stop-loss order / TAKE_PROFIT: Limit take-profit order / TRIGGER_LIMIT: Stop-limit order with trigger / TRIGGER_MARKET: Market order with trigger for stop-loss."},{"name":"positionId","type":"int64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"逐倉分倉模式下平倉必傳","en":"In the Separate Isolated mode, closing a position must be transmitted"}]},"response":{"info":"","info_en":"","list":[{"name":"symbol","type":"string","values":"","zh":"交易對, 例如: BTC-USDT","en":"trading pair, for example: BTC-USDT"},{"name":"side","type":"string","values":"","zh":"買賣方向","en":"buying and selling direction"},{"name":"type","type":"string","values":"","zh":"LIMIT：限價單/MARKET：市價單/STOP_MARKET：市價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET：市價止盈單/STOP：限價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT：限價止盈單/TRIGGER_LIMIT：計劃委託單限價單/TRIGGER_MARKET：計劃委託市價單/TRAILING_STOP_MARKET:追踪委託單/TRAILING_TP_SL:移動止盈止損","en":"LIMIT: Limit Order / MARKET: Market Order / STOP_MARKET: Stop Market Order / TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET: Take Profit Market Order / STOP: Stop Limit Order / TAKE_PROFIT: Take Profit Limit Order / TRIGGER_LIMIT: Stop Limit Order with Trigger / TRIGGER_MARKET: Stop Market Order with Trigger / TRAILING_STOP_MARKET: Trailing Stop Market Order / TRAILING_TP_SL: Trailing TakeProfit or StopLoss"},{"name":"positionSide","type":"string","values":"","zh":"持仓方向，单项持仓必填BOTH，双向持仓僅可選擇 LONG 或 SHORT，為空時默認LONG","en":"Position direction, required for single position as BOTH, for both long and short positions only LONG or SHORT can be chosen, defaults to LONG if empty"},{"name":"reduceOnly","type":"string","values":"","zh":"true, false; 單項持倉模式下默認false；雙開持倉模式下不接受此參數","en":"true, false; Default value is false for single position mode; This parameter is not accepted for both long and short positions mode"},{"name":"orderID","type":"string","values":"","zh":"訂單號","en":"Order ID"},{"name":"workingType","type":"string","values":"","zh":"stopPrice觸發價價格類型：MARK_PRICE、CONTRACT_PRICE、INDEX_PRICE，默認MARK_PRICE。當type為STOP或STOP_MARKET，以及stopGuaranteed為true的時候，workingType只能為CONTRACT_PRICE。","en":"StopPrice trigger price types: MARK_PRICE, CONTRACT_PRICE, INDEX_PRICE, default MARK_PRICE. When the type is STOP or STOP_MARKET, and stopGuaranteed is true, the workingType must only be CONTRACT_PRICE."},{"name":"clientOrderId","type":"string","values":"","zh":"用戶自定義訂單ID，系統會將該字段轉為英文小寫","en":"Customized order ID for users. The system will convert this field to lowercase."},{"name":"stopGuaranteed","type":"string","values":"","zh":"true：啟用保證止盈停損功能；false：不啟用保證停損功能；cutfee:啟用保證停損功能，同時啟用VIP保證停損費用減免功能，VIP費用減免只有在停損單時才起作用。預設不啟用保證止盈止損功能。支援的訂單類型type有：STOP_MARKET：市價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET：市價止盈單/STOP：限價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT：限價止盈單/TRIGGER_LIMIT：計劃委託單限價單/TRIGGER_MARKET：計劃計劃委託市價單。","en":"true: Enables the guaranteed stop-loss and take-profit feature; false: Disables the feature; cutfee: Enable the guaranteed stop loss function and enable the VIP guaranteed stop loss fee reduction function. The VIP fee reduction only takes effect when placing a stop loss order.. The guaranteed stop-loss feature is not enabled by default. Supported order types include: STOP_MARKET: Market stop-loss order / TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET: Market take-profit order / STOP: Limit stop-loss order / TAKE_PROFIT: Limit take-profit order / TRIGGER_LIMIT: Stop-limit order with trigger / TRIGGER_MARKET: Market order with trigger for stop-loss."},{"name":"status","type":"string","values":"","zh":"訂單狀態","en":"Order status"},{"name":"avgPrice","type":"string","values":"","zh":"平均成交價，type=MARKET時有值","en":"Average filled price, present when type=MARKET"},{"name":"executedQty","type":"string","values":"","zh":"成交數量，幣數","en":"Transaction quantity, coins"}]},"error":{"info":"","info_en":"","list":[{"code":"101204","msg":"Insufficient margin","description":{"zh":"保證金不足，無法完成下單操作。","en":"Insufficient margin to place the order."},"solution":{"zh":"請增加保證金、降低槓桿或減少下單數量後再試。","en":"Add margin, lower leverage, or reduce order size and retry."}},{"code":"109400","msg":"timestamp is invalid","description":{"zh":"請求中的 timestamp 參數不合法或與服務端時間偏差過大。","en":"The timestamp parameter is invalid or too far from server time."},"solution":{"zh":"請使用毫秒級時間戳，並校準本地時間。","en":"Use a millisecond timestamp and synchronize your system time."}},{"code":"101205","msg":"No position to close","description":{"zh":"當前無可用持倉，無法進行平倉操作。","en":"No position exists to close."},"solution":{"zh":"請先查詢持倉，確認存在持倉後再操作。","en":"Query positions first and retry only if a position exists."}},{"code":"109429","msg":"Too many repeated errors","description":{"zh":"短時間內多次提交相同錯誤請求，已被系統暫時限制。","en":"Too many repeated error requests in a short period."},"solution":{"zh":"請修正請求參數或訂單狀態，並在限制時間後重試。","en":"Fix the root cause and retry after the restriction period."}},{"code":"101253","msg":"Insufficient margin","description":{"zh":"保證金不足，當前資產無法支撐下單。","en":"Insufficient margin for the current order."},"solution":{"zh":"請補充資金或降低下單金額。","en":"Add funds or reduce order notional."}},{"code":"101400","msg":"clientOrderID unique check failed","description":{"zh":"clientOrderID 重複，唯一性校驗失敗。","en":"Duplicate clientOrderID detected."},"solution":{"zh":"請確保每筆訂單使用唯一的 clientOrderID。","en":"Ensure each order uses a unique clientOrderID."}},{"code":"110424","msg":"Order size exceeds available amount","description":{"zh":"下單數量或金額超過當前可用資產。","en":"Order size exceeds available balance."},"solution":{"zh":"請降低下單數量或增加可用資產。","en":"Reduce order size or add available balance."}},{"code":"109425","msg":"Trading pair does not exist","description":{"zh":"請求的交易對不存在或不支援。","en":"The requested trading pair does not exist or is not supported."},"solution":{"zh":"請先查詢合約列表接口，確認交易對是否有效。","en":"Query the contract list to verify the trading pair."}},{"code":"101212","msg":"Available amount is insufficient","description":{"zh":"可用資產不足以完成當前下單。","en":"Available balance is insufficient for this order."},"solution":{"zh":"請減少下單金額或補充資產。","en":"Reduce order amount or add funds."}},{"code":"101485","msg":"Order size below minimum","description":{"zh":"下單金額低於最小開倉限制。","en":"Order size is below the minimum required to open a position."},"solution":{"zh":"請提高下單金額至最小限制以上。","en":"Increase order size to meet the minimum requirement."}},{"code":"100004","msg":"Permission denied","description":{"zh":"API Key 未開通永續合約交易權限。","en":"The API key does not have perpetual futures trading permission."},"solution":{"zh":"請在 API Key 管理頁面開啟對應權限後重試。","en":"Enable the required permission for the API key and retry."}},{"code":"101209","msg":"Maximum position value reached","description":{"zh":"當前槓桿下倉位價值已達上限。","en":"The maximum position value for the current leverage has been reached."},"solution":{"zh":"請降低槓桿或減少下單金額。","en":"Lower leverage or reduce order size."}},{"code":"101222","msg":"Leverage risk too high","description":{"zh":"當前槓桿風險過高，已被限制下單。","en":"Current leverage poses high risk and order placement is restricted."},"solution":{"zh":"請降低槓桿後再試。","en":"Lower leverage and retry."}},{"code":"100413","msg":"Incorrect API key","description":{"zh":"提供的 API Key 不正確或已失效。","en":"The provided API key is incorrect or invalid."},"solution":{"zh":"請檢查 API Key 是否正確，並確認未被刪除。","en":"Verify the API key and ensure it is valid."}},{"code":"109420","msg":"Position not exist","description":{"zh":"當前交易對下不存在對應持倉。","en":"No position exists for the specified symbol."},"solution":{"zh":"請先查詢持倉信息後再進行操作。","en":"Query position information before performing this action."}},{"code":"101484","msg":"Advanced verification required","description":{"zh":"需完成高級身份認證後方可使用該服務。","en":"Advanced identity verification is required to use this service."},"solution":{"zh":"請完成高級 KYC 認證後再試。","en":"Complete advanced KYC verification and retry."}},{"code":"110411","msg":"Invalid Stop Loss price","description":{"zh":"止損價應低於當前價格（多單）。","en":"Stop Loss price should be lower than the current price for long positions."},"solution":{"zh":"請根據持倉方向重新設置止損價。","en":"Adjust the Stop Loss price according to the position side."}},{"code":"100410","msg":"Rate limited","description":{"zh":"請求頻率過高，已觸發限流。","en":"Request rate limit exceeded."},"solution":{"zh":"請降低請求頻率並稍後重試。","en":"Reduce request frequency and retry later."}},{"code":"100001","msg":"Signature verification failed","description":{"zh":"請求簽名校驗失敗。","en":"Signature verification failed."},"solution":{"zh":"請檢查簽名算法、參數排序及 API Secret 是否正確。","en":"Verify the signature algorithm, parameter order, and API secret."}},{"code":"110413","msg":"Invalid Take Profit price","description":{"zh":"止盈價應高於當前價格（多單）。","en":"Take Profit price should be greater than the current price for long positions."},"solution":{"zh":"請根據持倉方向重新設置止盈價。","en":"Adjust the Take Profit price according to the position side."}}]}},"info":{"en":[{"type":"div","info":"Signature Verification: Yes"},{"type":"div","info":"Applicable Accounts: Master and Sub Accounts"},{"type":"div","info":"API Key Permission: Professional Futures Trading"},{"type":"div","info":"Endpoint description:The current account places an order on the specified symbol contract. (Supports limit order, market order, market order for plan entrustment, limit order for plan entrustment, position stop profit and stop loss order, and liquidation for positions)"}],"zh":[{"type":"div","info":"是否驗簽: 是"},{"type":"div","info":"適用帳戶: 子母帳戶"},{"type":"div","info":"API Key权限: 專業合約交易"},{"type":"div","info":"接口描述：當前賬戶在指定symbol合約上進行下單操作。(支持限價單、市價單、計劃委託市價單、計劃委託限價單、倉位止盈止損單、針對倉位平倉)"}]}}


