module.exports = {"type":"REST","title":"下單","en":"Place order","api":{"uri":"/openApi/spot/v1/trade/order","method":"POST","rate-limitation":"10/second","ip-rate-limitation":"3","payload":[{"title":"MARKET","desc":"Place an order at the market price","payload":{"type":"MARKET","symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"BUY","quantity":0.002,"newClientOrderId":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"TAKE_STOP_MARKET","desc":"Market price stop profit and stop loss order","payload":{"type":"TAKE_STOP_MARKET","stopPrice":50000,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"SELL","quantity":0.002,"newClientOrderId":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"TAKE_STOP_LIMIT","desc":"Limit price, take profit and stop loss order","payload":{"type":"TAKE_STOP_LIMIT","price":60000,"stopPrice":70000,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"BUYE","quantity":0.002,"newClientOrderId":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"TRIGGER_LIMIT","desc":"TRIGGER LIMIT","payload":{"type":"TRIGGER_LIMIT","price":60000,"stopPrice":70000,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"BUY","quantity":0.002,"newClientOrderId":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","timestamp":1726223068783}},{"title":"TRIGGER_MARKET","desc":"TRIGGER MARKET","payload":{"type":"TRIGGER_MARKET","stopPrice":60000,"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"BUY","quantity":0.002,"positionSide":"LONG","newClientOrderId":"","recvWindow":1000,"timeInForce":"GTC","timestamp":1726223068783}}],"responseBody":{"code":0,"msg":"","debugMsg":"","data":{"symbol":"NEMS-USDT","orderId":1735963671248581000,"transactTime":1702720966528,"price":"0.1557","origQty":"115","executedQty":"0","cummulativeQuoteQty":"0","status":"PENDING","type":"LIMIT","side":"SELL"}},"request":{"info":["<div><b>註意</b></div>","<div>限價單必須傳price參數。</div>","<div>限價單必須傳quantity或quoteOrderQty其中一個，當兩個參數同時傳遞時，服務端優先使用參數quantity。</div>","<div>市價買單必須傳quoteOrderQty參數。</div>","<div>市價賣單必須傳quantity參數。</div>","<div><b>警告</b></div>","<div>如果需要計算最大最小下單幣對數量可使用公式：U (最小/最大下單金額) / (限價單輸入Limit price or 市價單Market price)</div>","<div><b>查詢價格可參考：</b> <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs/#/zh-tw/spot/market-api.html#24%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E8%AE%8A%E5%8B%95%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81' target='_blank'>GET /openApi/spot/v1/ticker/24hr</a></div>","<div><b>最小最大下單金額可參考：</b> <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs/#/zh-tw/spot/market-api.html#%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%81%E7%A8%AE' target='_blank'>GET /openApi/spot/v1/common/symbols</a></div>","<div><b>交易規則:</b></div>","<div><a href='https://bingx.com/zh-tw/spot/trading-rules/' target='_blank'>https://bingx.com/zh-tw/spot/trading-rules/</a></div>","<div><a href='https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/spot/v1/common/symbols' target='_blank'>關於價格精度和數量精度參考接口</a></div>","<div>如果精度超過當期的範圍，當前API下單仍然成功，但是會被截斷。比如price要求是:0.0001, 如果下單0.123456. 最後會以0.1234成功提交</div>","<div><h3>訂單類型</h3></div>","<div><p class='item-code-content'>MARKET:市價</br>LIMIT:限價</br>TAKE_STOP_LIMIT:限價止盈止損單</br>TAKE_STOP_MARKET:市價止盈止損單</br>TRIGGER_LIMIT：限價計畫委託</br>TRIGGER_MARKET：市價計畫委託</p></div>","<div><b>如果現貨帶單交易員並且打開了帶單功能</b></div>","<div>下單頻率只能1/s，超過會被限頻</div>","<div>買入可以通過本接口買入: <a href='/openApi/spot/v1/trade/order' target='_blank'>POST /openApi/spot/v1/trade/order</a></div>","<div>賣出需要另外一個特殊的接口賣出:最小最大下單金額可參考: <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs-v3/#/zh-tw/Copy%20Trade/Spot%20Trading/%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E6%8C%89%E8%B2%B7%E5%85%A5%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%E8%99%9F%E8%B3%A3%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E8%B4%A7%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2' target='_blank'>POST /openApi/copyTrading/v1/spot/trader/sellOrder</a></div>"],"info_en":["<div><b>Notice:</b></div>","<div>For limit orders, price is required.</div>","<div>For limit orders, either quantity or quoteOrderQty is required. When two parameters are passed at the same time, the server uses the parameter quantity first.</div>","<div>For buy-side market orders, quoteOrderQty is required.</div>","<div>For sell-side market orders, quantity is required.</div>","<div><b>Trading Rules:</b></div>","<div><a href='https://bingx.com/en/spot/trading-rules/' target='_blank'>https://bingx.com/en/spot/trading-rules/</a></div>","<div><a href='https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/spot/v1/common/symbols' target='_blank'>About price accuracy and quantity accuracy reference interface</a></div>","<div>If the accuracy exceeds the range of the current period, the current API order will still be successful, but it will be truncated. For example, the price requirement is: 0.0001, if the order is 0.123456, it will be successfully submitted with 0.1234.</div>","<div><b>For price reference, please check:</b> <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs/#/en-us/spot/market-api.html#24-hour%20price%20changes' target='_blank'>GET /openApi/spot/v1/ticker/24hr</a></div>","<div><b>For Minimum/Maximum transaction amount reference, please check:</b> <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs/#/en-us/spot/market-api.html#Query%20Symbols' target='_blank'>GET /openApi/spot/v1/common/symbols</a></div>","<div><b>If the spot trader of copy trading has enabled the function</b></div>","<div>The order frequency can only be 1/s, exceeding it will be limited frequency.</div>","<div>BUY can use this endpoint: POST /openApi/spot/v1/trade/order</div>","<div>SELL need to use another specific endpoint: <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs-v3/#/en/Copy%20Trade/Spot%20Trading/Trader%20sells%20spot%20assets%20based%20on%20buy%20order%20number' target='_blank'>POST /openApi/copyTrading/v1/spot/trader/sellOrder</a></div>"],"list":[{"name":"symbol","type":"string","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"交易品種, 例如: BTC-USDT, 請使用大寫字母","en":"Trading pair, e.g., BTC-USDT"},{"name":"side","type":"string","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"交易類型, BUY買 SELL賣","en":"BUY/SELL"},{"name":"type","type":"string","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"MARKET/LIMIT/TAKE_STOP_LIMIT/TAKE_STOP_MARKET/TRIGGER_LIMIT/TRIGGER_MARKET","en":"MARKET/LIMIT/TAKE_STOP_LIMIT/TAKE_STOP_MARKET/TRIGGER_LIMIT/TRIGGER_MARKET"},{"name":"stopPrice","type":"string","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"觸發價格，用於TAKE_ STOP_ LIMIT， TAKE_ STOP_ MARKET，TRIGGER_ LIMIT，TRIGGER_ MARKET類型的訂單。","en":"order trigger price, used for TAKE_ STOP_ LIMITED,TAKE_ STOP_ MARKET, TRIGGER_ LIMITED, TRIGGER_ Market type orders."},{"name":"quantity","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"下單數量, 例如: 0.1BTC","en":"Original quantity, e.g., 0.1BTC"},{"name":"quoteOrderQty","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"下單金額, 例如: 100USDT,如果quantity 和 quoteOrderQty 同時輸入，優先使用quantity，quoteOrderQty會被丟棄","en":"Quote order quantity, e.g., 100USDT,if quantity and quoteOrderQty are input at the same time, quantity will be used first, and quoteOrderQty will be discarded"},{"name":"price","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"委託價格, 例如: 10000USDT","en":"Price, e.g., 10000USDT"},{"name":"newClientOrderId","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"只能字母、數字和_,用戶自定義訂單ID，限制字符長度1-40,不同訂單不可使用相同的newClientOrderId","en":"Only letters, numbers and _,Customized order ID for users, with a limit of characters from 1 to 40. Different orders cannot use the same newClientOrderId,Only supports a query range of 2 hours"},{"name":"timeInForce","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"有效方式，目前支持PostOnly、GTC、IOC、FOK,不填寫則默認GTC","en":"Time in force, currently supports PostOnly, GTC, IOC, FOK. Default is GTC if not specified."},{"name":"recvWindow","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"請求有效時間空窗值, 單位:毫秒","en":"Request valid time window value, Unit: milliseconds"},{"name":"timestamp","type":"int64","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"請求時間戳, 單位:毫秒","en":"Timestamp of initiating the request, Unit: milliseconds"}]},"response":{"info":"","info_en":"","list":[{