o":"A new status value (29: Pre-Delisted) has been added to the symbol list API. When a symbol is in Pre-Delisted (29) or Delisted (30) status, order placement requests will be blocked by the API service, while order cancellation is still allowed.","model":"Spot Trading","link":""},{"updateTime":"2026-01-05","path":"/openApi/swap/v2/trade/order","type":"Update","info":"Added order-by-quote functionality with the field quoteOrderQty.","model":"USDT-M Perpetual Contracts","link":""},{"updateTime":"2025-12-18","path":"/openApi/swap/v2/trade/getVst","type":"Upgraded","info":"Upgraded the futures demo VST claim endpoint from v1 to v2, adding support for increasing or decreasing custom amounts.","model":"Swap Trading","link":"#/en/Swap/Trades%20Endpoints/Apply%20VST"},{"updateTime":"2025-12-16","path":"-","type":"Update","info":"Removed IP rate limits for Account API Group [2] and Group [3]. The previous IP-based limits, including the total group limit (2000 requests per 10 seconds) and the per-endpoint limit (300 requests per 10 seconds), are no longer applied.","model":"API","link":""},{"updateTime":"2025-12-09","path":"/openApi/account/transfer/v1/subAccount/transferAsset","type":"Added","info":"Added the Sub-Mother Account Asset Transfer interface. This interface is only available to the parent account and is used for asset transfers between the parent account and sub-accounts.","model":"Sub-account Management","link":"#/en/Account%20&%20Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/Sub-Mother%20Account%20Asset%20Transfer%20Interface%20(Only%20for%20Parent%20Account%20Operations)"},{"updateTime":"2025-12-09","path":"/openApi/wallets/v1/capital/innerTransfer/apply","type":"Update","info":"The main account internal transfer API now supports transferring spot assets.","model":"Fund Account","link":"#/en/account-and-wallet/Fund%20Account/Main%20Accoun%20internal%20transfer"},{"updateTime":"2025-12-09","path":"/openApi/wallets/v1/capital/subAccountInnerTransfer/apply","type":"Update","i