module.exports = {"type":"REST","title":"批量下單","en":"Place multiple orders","api":{"uri":"/openApi/spot/v1/trade/batchOrders","method":"POST","rate-limitation":"2/second","ip-rate-limitation":"3","payload":{"data":"[{\"symbol\": \"ETH-USDT\", \"side\": \"BUY\", \"type\": \"LIMIT\", \"quantity\": 7.663, \"price\": 12.479, \"newClientOrderId\": \"\"}]","recvWindow":"60000"},"responseBody":{"code":0,"msg":"","debugMsg":"","data":{"orders":[{"symbol":"ETH-USDT","orderId":1735967859282101200,"transactTime":1702721965033,"price":"12.479","origQty":"7.663","executedQty":"0","cummulativeQuoteQty":"0","status":"PENDING","type":"LIMIT","side":"BUY","clientOrderID":""}]}},"request":{"info":["<div><b>註意</b></div>","<div>限價單必須傳price參數。</div>","<div>限價單必須傳quantity或quoteOrderQty其中一個，當兩個參數同時傳遞時，服務端優先使用參數quantity。</div>","<div>市價買單必須傳quoteOrderQty參數。</div>","<div>市價賣單必須傳quantity參數。</div>","<div>接口創建的訂單在APP和Web頁面不會顯示。</div>","<div><b>警告</b></div>","<div>如果需要計算最大最小下單幣對數量可使用公式：U (最小/最大下單金額) / (限價單輸入Limit price or 市價單Market price)</div>","<div><b>查詢價格可參考：</b> <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs/#/zh-tw/spot/market-api.html#24%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E8%AE%8A%E5%8B%95%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81' target='_blank'>GET /openApi/spot/v1/ticker/24hr</a></div>","<div><b>最小最大下單金額可參考：</b> <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs/#/zh-tw/spot/market-api.html#%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%81%E7%A8%AE' target='_blank'>GET /openApi/spot/v1/common/symbols</a></div>","<div><b>交易規則:</b></div>","<div><a href='https://bingx.com/zh-tw/spot/trading-rules/' target='_blank'>https://bingx.com/zh-tw/spot/trading-rules/</a></div>","<div><a href='https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/spot/v1/common/symbols' target='_blank'>關於價格精度和數量精度參考接口</a></div>","<div>如果精度超過當期的範圍，當前API下單仍然成功，但是會被截斷。比如price要求是:0.0001, 如果下單0.123456. 最後會以0.1234成功提交</div>","<div><li>批量下單, 如何對request簽名? 請參考 <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs/#/swapV2/trade-api.html#%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8B%E5%96%AE' target='_blank'>永續: 批量下單</a> </li></div>"],"info_en":["<div><b>Notes</b></div>","<div>For a limit order, the \"price\" parameter must be included.</div>","<div>For a limit order, either \"quantity\" or \"quoteOrderQty\" must be included. If both parameters are provided, the server will prioritize the \"quantity\" parameter.</div>","<div>For a market buy order, the \"quoteOrderQty\" parameter must be included.</div>","<div>For a market sell order, the \"quantity\" parameter must be included.</div>","<div>Orders created through the API will not be displayed on the app and web pages.</div>","<div><b>Warning</b></div>","<div>If you need to calculate the maximum and minimum order quantities for a currency pair, you can use the formula: U (minNotional or maxNotional) / (Limit price or Market price)</div>","<div><b>For price reference, please check:</b> <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs/#/en-us/spot/market-api.html#24-hour%20price%20changes' target='_blank'>GET /openApi/spot/v1/ticker/24hr</a></div>","<div><b>For Minimum/Maximum transaction amount reference, please check:</b> <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs/#/en-us/spot/market-api.html#Query%20Symbols' target='_blank'>GET /openApi/spot/v1/common/symbols</a></div>","<div><b>Trading Rules:</b></div>","<div><a href='https://bingx.com/en/spot/trading-rules/' target='_blank'>https://bingx.com/en/spot/trading-rules/</a></div>","<div><a href='https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/spot/v1/common/symbols' target='_blank'>About price accuracy and quantity accuracy reference interface</a></div>","<div>If the accuracy exceeds the range of the current period, the current API order will still be successful, but it will be truncated. For example, the price requirement is: 0.0001, if the order is 0.123456, it will be successfully submitted with 0.1234.</div>","<div><li>place batch orders, how to sign the request? please refer to <a href='https://bingx-api.github.io/docs/#/swapV2/trade-api.html#Bulk%20order'  target='_blank'>Perpetual: place batch orders</a> </li></div>"],"list":[{"name":"data","type":"array","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"下單的request數組","en":"The request array for placing orders, limited to 5 orders."},{"name":"sync","type":"bool","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"sync=false(如不填寫則默認false):並行下單(但是需要所有訂單的symbol/side/type相同),sync=true(多個訂單串行下單，所有訂單不要求symbol/side/type相同)","en":"sync=false (default false if not filled in): parallel ordering (but all orders need to have the same symbol/side/type), sync = true (multiple orders are ordered serially, all orders do not require the same symbol/side/type)"}]},"response":{"info":"","info_en":"","list":[{"name":"orders","type":"array","values":"","zh":"單個下單的response數組,限制5個訂單","en":"Response array for a single order"}]},"error":{"info":"","info_en":"","list":[]}},"info":{"en":[{"type":"div","info":"Signature Verification: Yes"},{"type":"div","info":"Applicable Accounts: Master and Sub Accounts"},{"type":"div","info":"API Key Permission: Spot Trading"},{"type":"div","info":"Endpoint description: Can be used to place orders in bulk on spot"}],"zh":[{"type":"div","info":"是否驗簽: 是"},{"type":"div","info":"適用帳戶: 子母帳戶"},{"type":"div","info":"API Key权限: 現貨交易"},{"type":"div","info":"接口描述: 可用於在現貨批量下單"}]}}


