module.exports = {"type":"REST","title":"測試下單","en":"Test Order","api":{"uri":"/openApi/swap/v2/trade/order/test","method":"POST","rate-limitation":"5/second","ip-rate-limitation":"2","payload":{"symbol":"BTC-USDT","side":"BUY","positionSide":"LONG","type":"MARKET","quantity":5,"takeProfit":"{\"type\": \"TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET\", \"stopPrice\": 31968.0,\"price\": 31968.0,\"workingType\":\"MARK_PRICE\"}"},"responseBody":{"code":0,"msg":"","data":{"order":{"symbol":"BTC-USDT","orderId":1735950529123455000,"side":"BUY","positionSide":"LONG","type":"MARKET","clientOrderId":"","workingType":"MARK_PRICE"}}},"request":{"info":["<div>基於訂單 type 不同，強制要求某些參數:</div>","<div><li>LIMIT: 強制要求參數 quantity, price</li></div>","<div><li>MARKET: 強制要求參數 quantity</li></div>","<div><li>TRAILING_STOP_MARKET（追跡委託單）和TRAILING_TP_SL（移動止盈止損單）：需填寫price欄位或者priceRate欄位</li></div>","<div><li>TRIGGER_LIMIT, STOP, TAKE_PROFIT: 強制要求參數 quantity、stopPrice、price</li></div>","<div><li>STOP_MARKET, TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET, TRIGGER_MARKET: 強制要求參數 quantity、stopPrice</li></div>","<div>條件單的觸發必須:</div>","<div><h3>STOP/STOP_MARKET 止損單:</h3></div>","<div><li>已掛止損單累加數量不能大於持倉數量</li></div>","<div><li>買入: 標記價格高於等於觸發價stopPrice</li></div>","<div><li>賣出: 標記價格低於等於觸發價stopPrice</li></div>","<div><h3>TAKE_PROFIT/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET 止盈單:</h3></div>","<div><li>已掛止盈單累加數量不能大於持倉數量</li></div>","<div><li>買入: 標記價格低於等於觸發價stopPrice</li></div>","<div><li>賣出: 標記價格高於等於觸發價stopPrice</li></div>","<div>最小下單數量可從接口 /openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts 獲取:tradeMinQuantity、tradeMinUSDT</div>","<div><b>交易規則:</b></div>","<div><a href='https://bingx.com/zh-tw/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/' target='_blank'>https://bingx.com/zh-tw/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/</a></div>","<div>關於價格精度和數量精度參考接口: <a href='https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts' target='_blank'>https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts</a></div>","<div>如果精度超過當期的範圍，當前API下單仍然成功，但是會被截斷.比如price要求是:0.0001,如果下單0.123456.最後會以0.1234成功提交</div>"],"info_en":["<div>The participation and return are consistent with the ordering interface, but the actual order will not be placed, only the test results will be returned. The result is a fake order, and your funds will not be deducted. It will not appear on the real transaction panel and is only used to help you practice using the order interface</div>","<div>Depending on the order type, certain parameters are mandatory:</div>","<div><li>LIMIT: Mandatory Parameters: quantity, price</li></div>","<div><li>MARKET: Mandatory Parameters: quantity</li></div>","<div><li>TRAILING_STOP_MARKET (Tracking Stop Loss Order) or TRAILING_TP_SL (Trailing TakeProfit/StopLoss Order): The price field or priceRate field needs to be filled in</li></div>","<div><li>TRIGGER_LIMIT, STOP, TAKE_PROFIT: Mandatory Parameters: quantity, stopPrice, price</li></div>","<div><li>STOP_MARKET, TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET, TRIGGER_MARKET: Mandatory Parameters: quantity, stopPrice</li></div>","<div>The triggering of the conditional order must:</div>","<div><h3>STOP/STOP_MARKET stop loss order:</h3></div>","<div><li>The accumulative quantity of the pending stop loss orders cannot be greater than the quantity of open positions</li></div>","<div><li>Buy: the mark price is higher than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li></div>","<div><li>Sell: the mark price is lower than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li></div>","<div><h3>TAKE_PROFIT/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET take profit order:</h3></div>","<div><li>The accumulative quantity of the pending take profit order cannot be greater than the position quantity</li></div>","<div><li>Buy: the mark price is lower than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li></div>","<div><li>Sell: the mark price is higher than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li></div>","<div>The minimum order quantity can be obtained from the api /openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts: tradeMinQuantity, tradeMinUSDT</div>","<div><b>Trading Rules:</b></div>","<div><a href='https://bingx.com/en/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/' target='_blank'>https://bingx.com/en/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/</a></div>","<div>About price accuracy and quantity accuracy reference interface: <a href='https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts' target='_blank'>https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts</a></div>","<div>If the accuracy exceeds the range of the current period, the current API order will still be successful, but it will be truncated. For example, the price requirement is: 0.0001, if the order is 0.123456, it will be successfully submitted with 0.1234.</div>"],"list":[{"name":"symbol","type":"string","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"交易對, 例如: BTC-USDT, 請使用大寫字母","en":"There must be a hyphen/ \"-\" in the trading pair symbol. eg: BTC-USDT"},{"name":"type","type":"string","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"LIMIT：限價單/MARKET：市價單/STOP_MARKET：市價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET：市價止盈單/STOP：限價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT：限價止盈單/TRIGGER_LIMIT：計劃委託單限價單/TRIGGER_MARKET：計劃委託市價單/TRAILING_STOP_MARKET:追蹤委託單/TRAILING_TP_SL:移動止盈止損","en":"LIMIT: Limit Order / MARKET: Market Order / STOP_MARKET: Stop Market Order / TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET: Take Profit Market Order / STOP: Stop Limit Order / TAKE_PROFIT: Take Profit Limit Order / TRIGGER_LIMIT: Stop Limit Order with Trigger / TRIGGER_MARKET: Stop Market Order with Trigger / TRAILING_STOP_MARKET: Trailing Stop Market Order / TRAILING_TP_SL: Trailing TakeProfit or StopLoss"},{"name":"side","type":"string","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"買賣方向 SELL, BUY","en":"buying and selling direction SELL, BUY"},{"name":"positionSide","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"持仓方向，单项持仓必填BOTH，双向持仓僅可選擇 LONG 或 SHORT，為空時默認LONG","en":"Position direction, required for single position as BOTH, for both long and short positions only LONG or SHORT can be chosen, defaults to LONG if empty"},{"name":"reduceOnly","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"true, false; 單項持倉模式下默認false；雙開持倉模式下不接受此參數","en":"true, false; Default value is false for single position mode; This parameter is not accepted for both long and short positions mode"},{"name":"price","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"委託價格，TRAILING_STOP_MARKET和TRAILING_TP_SL類型傳該參數表示回撤價差","en":"Price, represents the trailing stop distance in TRAILING_STOP_MARKET and TRAILING_TP_SL"},{"name":"quantity","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"下單數量,合約數量，當前只支持以幣計的合約數，暫不支持用U的數量下單","en":"Original quantity, only support units by COIN ,Ordering with quantity U is not currently supported."},{"name":"stopPrice","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"觸發價, 僅 STOP_MARKET,TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET,STOP,TAKE_PROFIT,TRIGGER_LIMIT,TRIGGER_MARKET 需要此參數","en":"Trigger price, only required for STOP_MARKET, TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET, STOP, TAKE_PROFIT, TRIGGER_LIMIT, TRIGGER_MARKET"},{"name":"priceRate","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"針對type:TRAILING_STOP_MARKET和TRAILING_TP_SL； 最大：1","en":"For type: TRAILING_STOP_MARKET or TRAILING_TP_SL; Maximum: 1"},{"name":"timestamp","type":"int64","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"請求的時間戳，單位:毫秒","en":"request timestamp, unit: millisecond"},{"name":"stopLoss","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"支持下單同時設置止損。但僅支持type: STOP_MARKET/STOP","en":"Support setting stop loss while placing an order. Only supports type: STOP_MARKET/STOP"},{"name":"takeProfit","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"支持下單同時設置止盈。但僅支持type: TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET/TAKE_PROFIT","en":"Support setting take profit while placing an order. Only supports type: TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET/TAKE_PROFIT"},{"name":"clientOrderId","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"用戶自定義訂單ID，限制字符長度1-40,不同訂單不可使用相同的clientOrderId","en":"Customized order ID for users, with a limit of characters from 1 to 40. Different orders cannot use the same clientOrderId"},{"name":"recvWindow","type":"int64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"請求有效時間空窗值, 單位:毫秒","en":"Request valid time window value, Unit: milliseconds"},{"name":"timeInForce","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"有效方式，目前支持PostOnly、GTC、IOC和FOK","en":"Time in Force, currently supports PostOnly, GTC, IOC, and FOK"},{"name":"closePosition","type":"string","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"true, false；觸發後全部平倉，僅支援STOP_MARKET和TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET；不與quantity合用；自帶只平倉效果，不與reduceOnly 合用","en":"true, false; all position squaring after triggering, only support STOP_MARKET and TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET; not used with quantity; comes with only position squaring effect, not used with reduceOnly"},{"name":"activationPrice","type":"float64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"追蹤委託單/移動止盈止損單啟動價格，TRAILING_TP_SL和TRAILING_STOP_MARKET 需要此參數, 預設為下單當前市場價格(支援不同workingType)","en":"Used with TRAILING_STOP_MARKET or TRAILING_TP_SL orders, default as the latest price(supporting different workingType)"}]},"response":{"info":"","info_en":"","list":[{"name":"symbol","type":"string","values":"","zh":"交易對, 例如: BTC-USDT","en":"trading pair, for example: BTC-USDT"},{"name":"side","type":"string","values":"","zh":"買賣方向","en":"buying and selling direction"},{"name":"type","type":"string","values":"","zh":"LIMIT：限價單/MARKET：市價單/STOP_MARKET：市價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET：市價止盈單/STOP：限價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT：限價止盈單/TRIGGER_LIMIT：計劃委託單限價單/TRIGGER_MARKET：計劃委託市價單/TRAILING_STOP_MARKET:追蹤委託單/TRAILING_TP_SL:移動止盈止損","en":"LIMIT: Limit Order / MARKET: Market Order / STOP_MARKET: Stop Market Order / TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET: Take Profit Market Order / STOP: Stop Limit Order / TAKE_PROFIT: Take Profit Limit Order / TRIGGER_LIMIT: Stop Limit Order with Trigger / TRIGGER_MARKET: Stop Market Order with Trigger / TRAILING_STOP_MARKET: Trailing Stop Market Order / TRAILING_TP_SL: Trailing TakeProfit or StopLoss"},{"name":"positionSide","type":"string","values":"","zh":"持仓方向，单项持仓必填BOTH，双向持仓僅可選擇 LONG 或 SHORT，為空時默認LONG","en":"Position direction, required for single position as BOTH, for both long and short positions only LONG or SHORT can be chosen, defaults to LONG if empty"},{"name":"reduceOnly","type":"string","values":"","zh":"true, false; 單項持倉模式下默認false；雙開持倉模式下不接受此參數","en":"true, false; Default value is false for single position mode; This parameter is not accepted for both long and short positions mode"},{"name":"orderId","type":"int64","values":"","zh":"訂單號","en":"Order ID"},{"name":"clientOrderId","type":"string","values":"","zh":"用戶自定義訂單ID","en":"Customized order ID for users"}]},"error":{"info":"","info_en":"","list":[{"code":"100001","msg":"Signature verification failed","description":{"zh":"簽名校驗失敗，請求簽名與服務端計算結果不一致。","en":"Signature verification failed. The request signature does not match the server-calculated signature."},"solution":{"zh":"請檢查簽名算法、參數排序、時間戳與密鑰是否正確，並參考官方示例代碼重新生成簽名。","en":"Verify the signature algorithm, parameter order, timestamp, and API secret. Refer to the official sample code to regenerate the signature."}},{"code":"100413","msg":"Incorrect API key","description":{"zh":"提供的 API Key 不正確，或已被刪除、失效。","en":"The provided API key is incorrect, deleted, or invalid."},"solution":{"zh":"請確認使用的是正確且有效的 API Key，並檢查是否來自對應的賬戶。","en":"Ensure the API key is correct, active, and belongs to the intended account."}},{"code":"100004","msg":"Permission denied","description":{"zh":"當前 API Key 未配置該接口所需的權限。","en":"The API key does not have the required permission for this endpoint."},"solution":{"zh":"請在 API Key 管理頁面開啟對應權限（如永續合約交易權限）後再重試。","en":"Enable the required permission (e.g. Perpetual Futures Trading) for the API key and retry."}},{"code":"109400","msg":"Invalid parameters","description":{"zh":"請求參數不完整或不合法，缺少必要字段（如 positionSide）。","en":"Invalid or missing request parameters. Required fields (e.g. positionSide) are missing."},"solution":{"zh":"請檢查接口文檔，補齊必填參數後再發送請求。","en":"Check the API documentation and provide all required parameters before retrying."}}]}},"info":{"en":[{"type":"div","info":"Signature Verification: Yes"},{"type":"div","info":"Applicable Accounts: Master and Sub Accounts"},{"type":"div","info":"API Key Permission: Professional Futures Trading"},{"type":"div","info":"Endpoint description:The current account places an order on the specified symbol contract. (Supports limit order, market order, market order for plan entrustment, limit order for plan entrustment, position stop profit and stop loss order, and liquidation for positions)"}],"zh":[{"type":"div","info":"是否驗簽: 是"},{"type":"div","info":"適用帳戶: 子母帳戶"},{"type":"div","info":"API Key权限: 專業合約交易"},{"type":"div","info":"接口描述：當前賬戶在指定symbol合約上進行下單操作。(支持限價單、市價單、計劃委託市價單、計劃委託限價單、倉位止盈止損單、針對倉位平倉)"}]}}


