der on the specified symbol contract. (Supports limit orders, market orders, planned entrusted market orders, planned entrusted limit orders, position stop-profit and stop-loss orders, and position closing.)"},{"type":"div","info":"<b>HTTP Request</b>"},{"type":"div","info":"<b>Warning:</b> Depending on the order type, certain parameters are mandatory:"},{"type":"div","info":"<li>LIMIT: Mandatory parameters: quantity, price</li>"},{"type":"div","info":"<li>MARKET: Mandatory parameters: quantity</li>"},{"type":"div","info":"<h3>1. Opening/closing a position: How to use the same api to open a position (long/short) and close a position (long/short)? Please refer to the following request payload combination:</h3>"},{"type":"div","info":"<p class='item-code-content'>open/buy LONG: side=BUY & positionSide=LONG</br>close/sell LONG: side=SELL & positionSide=LONG </br> open/sell SHORT: side=SELL & positionSide=SHORT</br>close/buy SHORT: side=BUY & positionSide=SHORT</P>"},{"type":"div","info":"<p class='item-code-content'>{\"symbol\": \"ETH-USD\",\"side\": \"BUY\",\"positionSide\": \"LONG\", \"type\": \"MARKET\", \"quantity\": 5}</P>"},{"type":"div","info":"<h3>2. Set take-profit and stop-loss separately: This api can also be used to set take-profit and stop-loss separately, but you need to open a position first;</h3>"},{"type":"div","info":"<p class='item-code-content'>{\"symbol\": \"ETH-USD\",\"side\": \"BUY\",\"positionSide\": \"LONG\", \"type\": \"TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET\", \"quantity\": 3, \"stopPrice\": 31968.0}</P>"},{"type":"div","info":"<h3>3. Set take profit and stop loss when opening and adding positions: use takeProfit or stopLoss field</h3>"},{"type":"div","info":"<p class='item-code-content'>{\"symbol\": \"BTC-USD\",\"side\": \"BUY\",\"positionSide\": \"LONG\",\"type\": \"MARKET\",\"quantity\": 5,\"takeProfit\": \"{\\\"type\\\": \\\"TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET\\\", \\\"stopPrice\\\": 31968.0,\\\"price\\\": 31968.0,\\\"workingType\\\":\\\"MARK_PRICE\\\"}\"}</P>"},{"type":"div","info":"<b>Warning:</b> The triggering of a conditional order must:"},{"type":"div","info":"<h3>STOP/STOP_MARKET Stop loss order:</h3>"},{"type":"div","info":"<li>The cumulative quantity of placed stop-loss orders cannot be greater than the position quantity</li>"},{"type":"div","info":"<li>Buy: The mark price is higher than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li>"},{"type":"div","info":"<li>Sell: The mark price is lower than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li>"},{"type":"div","info":"<h3>TAKE_PROFIT/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET Take profit order:</h3>"},{"type":"div","info":"<li>The cumulative quantity of pending stop-profit orders cannot be greater than the position quantity</li>"},{"type":"div","info":"<li>Buy: The mark price is lower than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li>"},{"type":"div","info":"<li>Sell: The mark price is higher than or equal to the trigger price stopPrice</li>"}],"zh":[{"type":"div","info":"是否驗簽: 是"},{"type":"div","info":"適用帳戶: 子母帳戶"},{"type":"div","info":"API Key权限: 讀取"},{"type":"div","info":"接口描述：交易下單"}]}}


