module.exports = {"type":"REST","title":"批量下單","en":"Place multiple orders","api":{"uri":"/openApi/swap/v2/trade/batchOrders","method":"POST","rate-limitation":"5/second","ip-rate-limitation":"3","payload":{"batchOrders":"[{\"symbol\": \"ETH-USDT\",\"type\": \"MARKET\",\"side\": \"BUY\",\"positionSide\": \"LONG\",\"quantity\": 1},{\"symbol\": \"BTC-USDT\",\"type\": \"MARKET\",\"side\": \"BUY\",\"positionSide\": \"LONG\",\"quantity\": 0.001}]"},"responseBody":{"code":0,"msg":"","data":{"orders":[{"symbol":"ID-USDT","orderId":1736010300483712300,"side":"SELL","positionSide":"LONG","type":"MARKET","clientOrderId":"","workingType":""}]}},"request":{"info":["<div><li>具體訂單條件規則，與普通下單一致</li></div>","<div><li>batchOrders是數組</li></div>","<div><li>批量下單的簽名可能稍微複雜，但是不用擔心, 可以參照以下四個步驟:</li></div>","<div><li>1. 把你的整個request body 變成 request query string如下</li></div>","<div><code>原始的 parameters: batchOrders=[{\"symbol\":\"ETH-USDT\",\"type\":\"MARKET\",\"side\":\"BUY\",\"positionSide\":\"LONG\",\"quantity\":1},{\"symbol\":\"BTC-USDT\",\"type\":\"MARKET\",\"side\":\"BUY\",\"positionSide\":\"LONG\",\"quantity\":0.001}]&timestamp=1692956597902</code></div>","<div><li>2. 對原始的 parameters 進行簽名</li></div>","<div><code>得到簽名: bab521321a62a1381a76b485b92dd0f4a8b16b4616cfa4c75ffba899f80dfc86</code></div>","<div><li>3.對請求參數的每一個值都進行URL編碼,比如字段batchOrders的值,這裡只對值value進行URL編碼，不對字段key進行URL編碼,也不是對整個原始的parameters字符串進行URL編碼，這裡有個特殊字段:timestamp的value也不用URL編碼，然後逐個替換成如下:</li></div>","<div><code>經過URL編碼value替換後: batchOrders=%5B%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22ETH-USDT%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22MARKET%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22positionSide%22%3A%22LONG%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A1%7D%2C%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22BTC-USDT%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22MARKET%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22positionSide%22%3A%22LONG%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A0.001%7D%5D&timestamp=1692956597902</code></div>","<div><li> 4. 最後的請求應該如下</li></div>","<div><code>POST https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/trade/batchOrders?batchOrders=%5B%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22ETH-USDT%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22MARKET%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22positionSide%22%3A%22LONG%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A1%7D%2C%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22BTC-USDT%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22MARKET%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22positionSide%22%3A%22LONG%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A0.001%7D%5D&timestamp=1692956597902&signature=bab521321a62a1381a76b485b92dd0f4a8b16b4616cfa4c75ffba899f80dfc86</code></div>","<div><b>警告:</b></div>","<div><li>批量下單採取併發處理，不保證訂單撮合順序</li></div>","<div><li>最小下單數量可從接口 /openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts 獲取:tradeMinQuantity、tradeMinUSDT</li></div>","<div><b>交易規則:</b></div>","<div><a href='https://bingx.com/zh-tw/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/' target='_blank'>https://bingx.com/zh-tw/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/</a></div>","<div><a href='https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts' target='_blank'>https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts</a></div>","<div>如果精度超過當期的範圍，當前API下單仍然成功，但是會被截斷.比如price要求是:0.0001,如果下單0.123456.最後會以0.1234成功提交</div>"],"info_en":["<div><li>Specific order conditions and rules are consistent with ordinary orders</li></div>","<div><li>BatchOrders is kind of difficult but do not worry, please refer to 4 steps below:</li></div>","<div><li>1. Make your payload to string</li></div>","<div><code>original parameters: batchOrders=[{\"symbol\":\"ETH-USDT\",\"type\":\"MARKET\",\"side\":\"BUY\",\"positionSide\":\"LONG\",\"quantity\":1},{\"symbol\":\"BTC-USDT\",\"type\":\"MARKET\",\"side\":\"BUY\",\"positionSide\":\"LONG\",\"quantity\":0.001}]&timestamp=1692956597902</code></div>","<div><li>2. Sign original parameters</li></div>","<div><code>signature: bab521321a62a1381a76b485b92dd0f4a8b16b4616cfa4c75ffba899f80dfc86</code></div>","<div><li>3. URL encode each value, for example the value of batchOrders field, except timestamp field value (do not URL encode the key, not URL encode the entire original parameters), make it like below:</li></div>","<div><code>after URL encoded: batchOrders=%5B%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22ETH-USDT%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22MARKET%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22positionSide%22%3A%22LONG%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A1%7D%2C%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22BTC-USDT%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22MARKET%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22positionSide%22%3A%22LONG%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A0.001%7D%5D&timestamp=1692956597902</code></div>","<div><li>4. The final request should be like</li></div>","<div><code>POST https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/trade/batchOrders?batchOrders=%5B%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22ETH-USDT%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22MARKET%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22positionSide%22%3A%22LONG%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A1%7D%2C%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22BTC-USDT%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22MARKET%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22positionSide%22%3A%22LONG%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A0.001%7D%5D&timestamp=1692956597902&signature=bab521321a62a1381a76b485b92dd0f4a8b16b4616cfa4c75ffba899f80dfc86</code></div>","<div><b>Warning:</b></div>","<div><li>Batch orders are processed concurrently, and order matching order is not guaranteed</li></div>","<div><li>The minimum order quantity can be obtained from the API /openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts: tradeMinQuantity, tradeMinUSDT</li></div>","<div><b>Trading Rules:</b></div>","<div><a href='https://bingx.com/en/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/' target='_blank'>https://bingx.com/en/tradeInfo/perpetual/trading-rules/BTC-USDT/</a></div>","<div><a href='https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts' target='_blank'>https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/swap/v2/quote/contracts</a></div>","<div>If the accuracy exceeds the range of the current period, the current API order will still be successful, but it will be truncated. For example, the price requirement is: 0.0001, if the order is 0.123456, it will be successfully submitted with 0.1234.</div>"],"list":[{"name":"batchOrders","type":"LIST<Order>","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"訂單列表，最多支持5个訂單,Order對象參考單個交易下單","en":"Order list, supporting up to 5 orders, with Order objects referencing transactions to place orders"},{"name":"timestamp","type":"int64","required_zh":"是","required_en":"Yes","values":"","zh":"請求的時間戳，單位:毫秒","en":"request timestamp, unit: millisecond"},{"name":"recvWindow","type":"int64","required_zh":"否","required_en":"No","values":"","zh":"請求有效時間空窗值, 單位:毫秒","en":"Request valid time window value, Unit: milliseconds"}]},"response":{"info":"","info_en":"","list":[{"name":"symbol","type":"string","values":"","zh":"交易對, 例如: BTC-USDT","en":"trading pair, for example: BTC-USDT"},{"name":"side","type":"string","values":"","zh":"買賣方向","en":"buying and selling direction"},{"name":"type","type":"string","values":"","zh":"LIMIT：限價單/MARKET：市價單/STOP_MARKET：市價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET：市價止盈單/STOP：限價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT：限價止盈單/TRIGGER_LIMIT：計劃委託單限價單/TRIGGER_MARKET：計劃委託市價單/TRAILING_STOP_MARKET:追踪委託單/TRAILING_TP_SL:移動止盈止損","en":"LIMIT: Limit Order / MARKET: Market Order / STOP_MARKET: Stop Market Order / TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET: Take Profit Market Order / STOP: Stop Limit Order / TAKE_PROFIT: Take Profit Limit Order / TRIGGER_LIMIT: Stop Limit Order with Trigger / TRIGGER_MARKET: Stop Market Order with Trigger / TRAILING_STOP_MARKET: Trailing Stop Market Order / TRAILING_TP_SL: Trailing TakeProfit or StopLoss"},{"name":"positionSide","type":"string","values":"","zh":"持仓方向，单项持仓必填BOTH，双向持仓僅可選擇 LONG 或 SHORT，為空時默認LONG","en":"Position direction, required for single position as BOTH, for both long and short positions only LONG or SHORT can be chosen, defaults to LONG if empty"},{"name":"reduceOnly","type":"string","values":"","zh":"true, false; 單項持倉模式下默認false；雙開持倉模式下不接受此參數","en":"true, false; Default value is false for single position mode; This parameter is not accepted for both long and short positions mode"},{"name":"orderID","type":"string","values":"","zh":"訂單號","en":"Order ID"},{"name":"workingType","type":"string","values":"","zh":"stopPrice觸發價價格類型：MARK_PRICE、CONTRACT_PRICE、INDEX_PRICE，默認MARK_PRICE。當type為STOP或STOP_MARKET，以及stopGuaranteed為true的時候，workingType只能為CONTRACT_PRICE。","en":"Customized order ID for users. The system will convert this field to lowercase."},{"name":"clientOrderId","type":"string","values":"","zh":"用戶自定義訂單ID，系統會將該字段轉為英文小寫","en":"true: Enables the guaranteed stop-loss and take-profit feature; false: Disables the feature. The guaranteed stop-loss feature is not enabled by default. Supported order types include: STOP_MARKET: Market stop-loss order / TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET: Market take-profit order / STOP: Limit stop-loss order / TAKE_PROFIT: Limit take-profit order / TRIGGER_LIMIT: Stop-limit order with trigger / TRIGGER_MARKET: Market order with trigger for stop-loss."},{"name":"stopGuaranteed","type":"string","values":"","zh":"true：啟用保證止盈停損功能；false：不啟用保證停損功能。預設不啟用保證止盈止損功能。支援的訂單類型type有：STOP_MARKET：市價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET：市價止盈單/STOP：限價止損單/TAKE_PROFIT：限價止盈單/TRIGGER_LIMIT：計劃委託單限價單/TRIGGER_MARKET：計劃計劃委託市價單。","en":"Order status"},{"name":"status","type":"string","values":"","zh":"訂單狀態","en":"Average filled price, present when type=MARKET"},{"name":"avgPrice","type":"string","values":"","zh":"平均成交價，type=MARKET時有值","en":"Transaction quantity, coins"}]},"error":{"info":"","info_en":"","list":[{"code":"109403","msg":"Risk forbidden","description":{"zh":"由於近期下單或撤單行為觸發風控規則，當前操作被限制。","en":"The operation is restricted due to risk control rules triggered by recent trading or cancellation behavior."},"solution":{"zh":"請降低下單與撤單頻率，稍後再試；如持續受限請聯繫客服。","en":"Reduce order and cancellation frequency and retry later. Contact support if the restriction persists."}},{"code":"112414","msg":"Total position amount reached platform limit","description":{"zh":"當前賬戶的總持倉規模已達到平台允許的上限。","en":"The total position amount of the account has reached the platform limit."},"solution":{"zh":"請先減少持倉或平倉後再下單。","en":"Reduce existing positions before placing new orders."}},{"code":"101400","msg":"Order amount below minimum","description":{"zh":"下單金額或名義價值低於該交易對允許的最小限制。","en":"The order amount or notional value is below the minimum allowed for the trading pair."},"solution":{"zh":"請提高下單數量或金額至最小限制以上。","en":"Increase the order size or notional to meet the minimum requirement."}},{"code":"109500","msg":"Invalid symbol format","description":{"zh":"交易對格式不正確，必須以 -USDT 或 -USDC 結尾。","en":"Invalid symbol format. The symbol must end with -USDT or -USDC."},"solution":{"zh":"請使用合約列表接口返回的標準交易對格式。","en":"Use symbols returned by the contracts endpoint with valid suffix."}},{"code":"100500","msg":"System busy","description":{"zh":"系統當前繁忙或下游服務異常，請求未能完成。","en":"The system is busy or a downstream service error occurred."},"solution":{"zh":"請稍後重試，如頻繁出現請聯繫技術支持。","en":"Retry later. Contact support if the issue persists."}},{"code":"110420","msg":"Invalid TP/SL or activation price","description":{"zh":"止盈、止損或激活價格與當前行情或持倉方向不符合要求。","en":"Take-profit, stop-loss, or activation price does not meet the requirements based on market price or position side."},"solution":{"zh":"請根據多空方向與標記價格重新設置 TP / SL / activationPrice。","en":"Adjust TP/SL/activationPrice according to position side and mark price."}}]}},"info":{"en":[{"type":"div","info":"Signature Verification: Yes"},{"type":"div","info":"Applicable Accounts: Master and Sub Accounts"},{"type":"div","info":"API Key Permission: Professional Futures Trading"},{"type":"div","info":"The current account performs batch order operations on the specified symbol contract"}],"zh":[{"type":"div","info":"是否驗簽: 是"},{"type":"div","info":"適用帳戶: 子母帳戶"},{"type":"div","info":"API Key权限: 專業合約交易"},{"type":"div","info":"當前賬戶在指定symbol合約上進行批量下單操作"}]}}


