module.exports = {"type":"DESCRIPTION","en":"SignAuth","title":"簽名認證","lines":{"zh":["<h2>簽名認證</h2>","<h3>創建 API Key</h3>","許多接口需要 API Key 才可以訪問。在對請求進行簽名之前，您必須通過 BingX 官網【用戶中心】-【<a href=\"https://bingx.com/zh-tc/accounts/api\" target=\"_blank\">API 管理</a>】創建 API Key。","創建完成後，您將獲得兩個重要信息：API Key 與 Secret Key，請妥善保管。","為了安全起見，建議在創建 API Key 時同時設置 IP 訪問白名單。","請勿將 API Key / Secret Key 泄露給任何第三方；若不慎泄露，請立即刪除並重新生成。","<h3>權限設置</h3>","新創建的 API Key 默認僅具有只讀權限。","如需通過 API 進行下單、撤單等寫操作，請在 UI 中為該 API Key 開啟相應權限。","<h3>請求要求</h3>","所有需要鑒權的接口請求必須包含以下信息：","請求 Header 中必須攜帶 X-BX-APIKEY，用於傳遞 API Key。","請求參數中必須攜帶 signature，該值由簽名算法計算得出。","timestamp 為請求時間戳（毫秒）。服務器會校驗該時間戳，若請求時間超過允許窗口（默認 5000ms），請求將被視為無效。該窗口可通過可選參數 recvWindow 調整。","<h3>簽名說明</h3>","signature 使用 HMAC-SHA256 算法對請求參數字串進行加密後得到，結果為 64 位十六進制小寫字串。","簽名計算與實際請求參數組裝遵循以下統一規則：","1. 取得所有業務參數（不包含 signature）。","2. 生成 timestamp（毫秒），並將其作為普通參數參與簽名與請求。","3. 將所有參數（業務參數 + timestamp）按參數名 key 進行 ASCII 升序排序。","4. 按排序後的順序拼接成 parameters 原文：","   key=value&key2=value2&...&timestamp=xxx","   該字串作為簽名原文，value 不做 URL 編碼。","5. 使用 secretKey 對 parameters 原文計算 HMAC-SHA256，得到 signature。","<h3>URL 編碼規則（僅適用於 Query String 傳參）</h3>","當接口要求以 query string（URL ?a=1&b=2...）方式傳參時，需遵循以下規則：","signature 始終基於未 URL Encode 的 parameters 原文計算。","若 parameters 原文中包含 '[' 或 '{'（通常表示參數值包含 JSON 或陣列字串），則在實際請求 URL 中只對每個參數的 value 進行 URL Encode。","僅對 value 進行 URL Encode，不對參數名 key 進行編碼。","URL Encode 使用 UTF-8 編碼，空格必須編碼為 %20。","若 parameters 原文中不包含 '[' 或 '{'，則實際請求 URL 中的 value 不需要進行 URL Encode。","<h3>Query String 發送示例</h3>","示例參數：","symbol=BTC-USDT","recvWindow=0","timestamp=1696751141337","1. 排序並拼接簽名原文 parameters：","recvWindow=0&symbol=BTC-USDT&timestamp=1696751141337","2. 使用 secretKey 生成簽名：","echo -n 'recvWindow=0&symbol=BTC-USDT&timestamp=1696751141337' | openssl dgst -sha256 -hmac 'SECRET_KEY' -hex","3. 發送請求：","https://open-api.bingx.com/xxx?recvWindow=0&symbol=BTC-USDT&timestamp=1696751141337&signature=...","<h3>包含 JSON 參數的 Query String 示例（批量下單）</h3>","示例請求 URL：","https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/spot/v1/trade/batchOrders?data=%5B%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22BTC-USDT%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22LIMIT%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A0.001%2C%22price%22%3A85000%2C%22newClientOrderId%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22BTC-USDT%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22LIMIT%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A0.001%2C%22price%22%3A42000%2C%22newClientOrderId%22%3A%22%22%7D%5D&recvWindow=60000&timestamp=1766679008165&signature=87bd22cfb380dddf8ce6d2901be7f107fef23dcf1e3d066e1519d1daa8fa81c6","說明：data 為 JSON 陣列字串，實際請求中僅對 value 做 URL Encode，signature 仍基於未編碼的 parameters 原文計算。","<h3>參數通過 request body 發送示例</h3>","以下示例適用於接口文檔明確要求 application/json，並從 request body 讀取參數的場景：","簽名參數（timestamp / signature）必須放在 request body 中，URL 不需要拼接 query。","示例業務參數：","{","  \"recvWindow\": 10000,","  \"symbol\": \"ETH-USDT\",","  \"type\": \"MARKET\",","  \"side\": \"SELL\",","  \"positionSide\": \"SHORT\",","  \"quantity\": 0.01","}","示例 request body：","{","  \"recvWindow\": 10000,","  \"symbol\": \"ETH-USDT\",","  \"type\": \"MARKET\",","  \"side\": \"SELL\",","  \"positionSide\": \"SHORT\",","  \"quantity\": 0.01,","  \"timestamp\": 1696751141337,","  \"signature\": \"xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\"","}","<h3>使用 Request Body 傳參的接口</h3>","以下接口使用 application/json 格式，參數通過 request body 傳遞：","<ul>","<li><a href=\"#/zh-tw/Account and Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/%E5%89%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AD%90%E8%B3%AC%E6%88%B6\">創建子賬戶</a> - <code>POST /openApi/subAccount/v1/create</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/zh-tw/Account and Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/%E5%89%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AD%90%E8%B3%AC%E6%88%B6apikey\">創建子賬戶apikey</a> - <code>POST /openApi/subAccount/v1/apiKey/create</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/zh-tw/Account and Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E5%AD%90%E8%B3%AC%E6%88%B6apikey\">編輯子賬戶apikey</a> - <code>POST /openApi/subAccount/v1/apiKey/edit</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/zh-tw/Account and Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E5%AD%90%E8%B3%AC%E6%88%B6apikey\">刪除子賬戶apikey</a> - <code>POST /openApi/subAccount/v1/apiKey/del</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/zh-tw/Account and Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/%E5%87%8D%E7%B5%90%20%E8%A7%A3%E5%87%8D%E5%AD%90%E8%B3%AC%E6%88%B6\">更新子賬戶狀態（凍結/解凍）</a> - <code>POST /openApi/subAccount/v1/updateStatus</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/zh-tw/Account%20and%20Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/查詢子母賬戶資金劃轉可劃轉金額\">查詢子母賬戶資金劃轉可劃轉金額</a> - <code>POST /openApi/account/transfer/v1/subAccount/transferAsset/supportCoins</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/zh-tw/Account%20and%20Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/子母賬號資產劃轉接口\">子母賬號資產劃轉</a> - <code>POST /openApi/account/transfer/v1/subAccount/transferAsset</code></li>","</ul>","<h3>請求交互</h3>","REST API 根 URL：https://open-api.bingx.com","備用域名：open-api.bingx.io（僅在主域名不可用時開放，總限頻 60/min）。","<h3>成功響應</h3>","HTTP 狀態碼 200 表示請求成功，返回內容將以 JSON 格式呈現。"],"en":["<h2>Signature Authentication</h2>","<h3>Generate an API Key</h3>","To access private endpoints, you must create an API Key on the BingX website under User Center → <a href=\"https://bingx.com/en/accounts/api\" target=\"_blank\">API Management</a>.","After creation, you will receive an API Key and a Secret Key. Please keep them secure.","For security reasons, it is strongly recommended to configure an IP whitelist.","Never disclose your API Key or Secret Key. If leaked, delete it immediately and create a new one.","<h3>Permission Settings</h3>","Newly created API Keys have read-only permission by default.","To place orders or perform other write operations, please enable the corresponding permissions in the UI.","<h3>Request Requirements</h3>","All authenticated REST requests must include:","X-BX-APIKEY in the request header.","signature as a request parameter, calculated using the signature algorithm.","timestamp (milliseconds) as the request time. Requests outside the allowed time window (default 5000ms) will be rejected. The window can be adjusted using recvWindow.","<h3>Signature Description</h3>","The signature is generated using HMAC-SHA256 and returned as a 64-character lowercase hexadecimal string.","The signing and request construction rules are as follows:","1. Collect all business parameters (excluding signature).","2. Generate timestamp (milliseconds) and include it as a normal parameter.","3. Sort all parameters (business parameters + timestamp) by key in ASCII ascending order.","4. Build the signing string:","   key=value&key2=value2&...&timestamp=xxx","   Parameter values must NOT be URL-encoded here.","5. Use secretKey to calculate HMAC-SHA256 over the signing string to obtain the signature.","<h3>URL Encoding Rules (Query String Only)</h3>","These rules apply only to query string parameters:","The signature is always calculated from the unencoded signing string.","If the signing string contains '[' or '{', URL-encode only parameter values in the actual request URL.","Do not encode parameter keys.","Use UTF-8 encoding and encode spaces as %20.","If the signing string does not contain '[' or '{', values do not need URL encoding.","<h3>Query String Example</h3>","Example parameters:","symbol=BTC-USDT","recvWindow=0","timestamp=1696751141337","Sorted signing string:","recvWindow=0&symbol=BTC-USDT&timestamp=1696751141337","Generate signature:","echo -n 'recvWindow=0&symbol=BTC-USDT&timestamp=1696751141337' | openssl dgst -sha256 -hmac 'SECRET_KEY' -hex","Send request:","https://open-api.bingx.com/xxx?recvWindow=0&symbol=BTC-USDT&timestamp=1696751141337&signature=...","<h3>Batch Order Query String Example</h3>","Example request URL:","https://open-api.bingx.com/openApi/spot/v1/trade/batchOrders?data=%5B%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22BTC-USDT%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22LIMIT%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A0.001%2C%22price%22%3A85000%2C%22newClientOrderId%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22symbol%22%3A%22BTC-USDT%22%2C%22side%22%3A%22BUY%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22LIMIT%22%2C%22quantity%22%3A0.001%2C%22price%22%3A42000%2C%22newClientOrderId%22%3A%22%22%7D%5D&recvWindow=60000&timestamp=1766679008165&signature=87bd22cfb380dddf8ce6d2901be7f107fef23dcf1e3d066e1519d1daa8fa81c6","<h3>Request Body Example</h3>","The following example applies to endpoints that require application/json and read parameters from the request body.","Signature parameters (timestamp / signature) must be included in the request body. Do not append them to the URL query.","Example business parameters:","{","  \"recvWindow\": 10000,","  \"symbol\": \"ETH-USDT\",","  \"type\": \"MARKET\",","  \"side\": \"SELL\",","  \"positionSide\": \"SHORT\",","  \"quantity\": 0.01","}","Example request body:","{","  \"recvWindow\": 10000,","  \"symbol\": \"ETH-USDT\",","  \"type\": \"MARKET\",","  \"side\": \"SELL\",","  \"positionSide\": \"SHORT\",","  \"quantity\": 0.01,","  \"timestamp\": 1696751141337,","  \"signature\": \"xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\"","}","<h3>Endpoints Using Request Body</h3>","The following endpoints use application/json format and send parameters via request body:","<ul>","<li><a href=\"#/en/Account and Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/%20Create%20Sub-account\">Create Sub-account</a> - <code>POST /openApi/subAccount/v1/create</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/en/Account and Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/%20Create%20Sub-account%20API%20Key\">Create Sub-account API Key</a> - <code>POST /openApi/subAccount/v1/apiKey/create</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/en/Account and Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/%20Edit%20Sub-Account%20API%20Key\">Edit Sub-Account API Key</a> - <code>POST /openApi/subAccount/v1/apiKey/edit</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/en/Account and Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/%20Delete%20Sub-Account%20API%20Key\">Delete Sub-Account API Key</a> - <code>POST /openApi/subAccount/v1/apiKey/del</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/en/Account and Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/%20Freeze%2FUnfreeze%20Sub-Account\">Update Sub-account Status (Freeze/Unfreeze)</a> - <code>POST /openApi/subAccount/v1/updateStatus</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/en/Account%20and%20Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/Query%20Sub-Mother%20Account%20Transferable%20Amount\">Query Sub-Mother Account Transferable Amount</a> - <code>POST /openApi/account/transfer/v1/subAccount/transferAsset/supportCoins</code></li>","<li><a href=\"#/en/Account%20and%20Wallet/Sub-account%20Management/Sub-Mother%20Account%20Asset%20Transfer%20Interface\">Sub-Mother Account Asset Transfer</a> - <code>POST /openApi/account/transfer/v1/subAccount/transferAsset</code></li>","</ul>","<h3>Success</h3>","An HTTP 200 status code indicates a successful response. The response body, if present, will be returned in JSON format."]},"api":{}}


